---
title: Hoisin Beef Udon with stir-fried broccolini
description: These sweet and salty beef noodles are sure to be a hit with table members of all ages. There's plenty of flavour, and with vibrant broccoli also featured, there are some nourishing elements too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R20_W34_IE_IEFB25883-2_Main__5high-01616188.jpg
